net.sf.mmm.util.property.api

Class AbstractRegularPropertyExpression<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.mmm.util.property.api.AbstractProperty<V>
      • net.sf.mmm.util.property.api.AbstractRegularPropertyExpression<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - is the generic type of the value.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, javafx.beans.Observable, javafx.beans.property.Property<V>, javafx.beans.property.ReadOnlyProperty<V>, javafx.beans.value.ObservableValue<V>, javafx.beans.value.WritableValue<V>, AttributeReadName, AttributeReadValue<V>, AttributeWriteValue<V>, PropertyPath<V>, ReadableProperty<V>, WritableProperty<V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BooleanPropertyExpression, IntegerPropertyExpression

    public abstract class AbstractRegularPropertyExpression<V>
extends AbstractProperty<V>
    This is the abstract base implementation of regular WritableProperty that has a value that is dynamically calculated. Here regular means that the value type is not special such as a Collection.
    Since:
    8.0.0
    Author:
    hohwille
